{"id": "1278378433201573961", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "开个小号回去坐牢嘛,又感觉没什么新鲜感<:Coffee:1240919421791375380>", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T15:39:29.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278455172174970982", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "1239255011037417497", "author_name": "mzmz07033", "author_bot": false, "content": "要是策划想弄得轻量化一点也不是不可以。。\n长草期弄点打王的材料关，上个厕所的时间就能搞定。再定时集中的来几次有主要剧情有难度有新机制的重大活动（可能一季度或者半年我认为都能接受），既照顾上班上学的玩家又让玩家有个盼头。\n忘却完全可以在这个基础上做的更有趣，机制活动的策划真得给美术音乐剧情几个组磕几个。。。", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T20:44:25.595000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278455825865904209", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "1239255011037417497", "author_name": "mzmz07033", "author_bot": false, "content": "小作坊就多点巧思取胜，别去学着大厂卷二次元工业产品，能力和技术差一点其实都没问题，用取巧的方法获胜才能活", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T20:47:01.447000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278456818196152431", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 0, "author_id": "1239255011037417497", "author_name": "mzmz07033", "author_bot": false, "content": "每次牢猫开问卷的时候我也会写点这个版本的小作文说说看法，也不知道他们到底看到没有，也没人给个答复🥲（我宁可不要那 200 银芯，只求他真的看到我写的。。。）", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T20:50:58.037000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1278460133185425502", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "PvE打到悶歡迎來PVP一起玩。以下是一些隊型推薦，歡迎你們再自己從中改出來花樣來，當然若只是領獎勵，這些也應該夠用了。\nWelcome to PVP. There are som suggestions for some typical team building. You can feel free to try if you have no idea about what a team can be. You can surely change from these to build your own one. I hope it is also helpful for you to enjoy the PVP or just to get the prize.\n\n基本概念／Basic rule of thumb\nPVP速度一般很快，頭五回合很常定勝負，一個成功的隊伍大多是有五回合內打殘對面的能力。看以下留言（主要方便我排位）\n\nPvp is quite speedy in general. For instance on Turn 5 the game is almost set. A good team should have the ability to call for the domination of the game by turn 5.（see the examples in the comment by me)", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:04:08.392000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:04:24.529000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 14}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1278460200977956895", "filename": "Screenshot_20240828_214719__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 128984, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1278460133185425502/1278460200977956895/Screenshot_20240828_214719__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb8e18&is=69ca3c98&hm=6f5701509c714f663053250bfc3627ac71c5734570b9d5091ab8e83681cd62b8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
{"id": "1278460281781227562", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:04:43.820000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1278460281852395612", "filename": "Screenshot_20240828_214719__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 128984, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1278460133185425502/1278460281852395612/Screenshot_20240828_214719__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb8e2b&is=69ca3cab&hm=8b450187bd0ffec493e06d7537457244583631742f68fddabd54ebdf6a582dd0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
{"id": "1278461577124773981", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "隊伍1／Team 1: 麻毒 Paratoxin\n由榜一 <@1247534528709398553> 所組，長年T1至T0的搭配，幾次被nerf後，命鑰未完全固定，但仍有強大的環境主宰能力，以上是我個人搭配，建議自己試一下。玩上去要有耐心，切記麻的傷害可以疊過一倍\n\nFound by our no.1 in the ranking <@1247534528709398553> , always T1 or even T0 in the PVP. After several nerfs, the team still demonstrate the ability to dominate the environment. The equipment is my personal choice. Feel free to change it by our own. The key of mastering it is to be patience and remember para dmg takes double on chara in para status", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:09:52.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1247534528709398553"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
{"id": "1278461741138710631", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:10:31.758000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1278461740933320806", "filename": "Screenshot_20240828_214827__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 130376, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1278460133185425502/1278461740933320806/Screenshot_20240828_214827__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb8f87&is=69ca3e07&hm=e3d6c81fe221817bdaddb8d2c49511a8db4c8544c24a17527481fbc1f6a72ff8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
{"id": "1278462646143946884", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "Team2 OTK Lily/OTK 莉莉\n我這個版本是來自<@1045141709580927067> 的這季版本。好玩之處就是把所有buff放在莉莉身上等一個全體攻擊OTK\n\nThe one I posted is found by <@1045141709580927067> in this new meta. If you have mostly all the buff for lily, you can do an OTK with Lily's AOE", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:14:07.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:16:14.690000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1045141709580927067"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
{"id": "1278466340201431051", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "Team3中速 Rhythm.\n這是我摸出來可以一戰的隊伍(薔薇騎士的構想來自 <@806384001895890965>，珊瑚靈感來自 <@655338276554801152> ），重點在於薔薇放在騎士就好，萊的大只用於復活，永夜都留給希萊，以及盡可能集火這四點。具體遊玩要一點實戰經驗.\n\nThis is the team I built myself that can somehow win games in the meta. Credit <@806384001895890965>  for the idea of using Rose with our little knight and credit <@655338276554801152>  for the idea of use of coral. The keys are: 1)put the rose equipment to Knight\n2)healer burst is only used for resurrection \n3)the resurrection key should put the dead healer with burst in highest priority \n4)Try to concentrate your dmg\nYou may need some experiences or trial to play this team", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:28:48.260000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152", "806384001895890965"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1278466339928805426", "filename": "Screenshot_20240828_214752__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 134211, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1278460133185425502/1278466339928805426/Screenshot_20240828_214752__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb93d0&is=69ca4250&hm=de8841fa787b54f75ac9383a417c7a1a55dec3fb8c397e11e1ed4cc2e6ef9af0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
