{"id": "1278467349095252050", "channel_id": "1278460133185425502", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "Team 4中速2 Rhythm2\n這是是另一種中速，上季已經有這樣類似的構築。有AOE和點殺和驅散是這副的賣點。\nThis is another typical rhythm changed from similar team last season. The main selling point is that it can fulfill the need of AOE or concentratring power or clear buff/debuff.", "timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:32:48.799000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-28T21:33:04.616000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278460133185425502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位基本型推介／PVP typical team suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681"]}
